Module java.base
Package java.lang.classfilePREVIEW

Class Attributes

java.lang.Object
java.lang.classfile.Attributes
public class Attributes extends Object
Attributes is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use Attributes when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
Attribute mappers for standard classfile attributes.
Since:
22
